      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Ndidi Onukwulu, known as Ndidi O, is a two-time JUNO-nominated and WCMA Blues Artist of the Year who has to date released five albums under her solo moniker and multiple singles as part of her trip-hop duo BOGA. She has toured nationally and internationally, playing festivals and concert halls. Her songs have been featured in numerous television programs and commercial campaigns, including those for GAP, Orange Is the New Black, The Flash (CW), Cloak & Dagger (Hulu), and most recently, Self Made: Inspired by the..."
      }
    ],
